an class="_ _5"></span>让这些人掏很多钱求</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y11e ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">保佑，结果钱却落入了他们的腰包…… </div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y11f ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这种现象特别可怕！<span class="_ _3"></span>作为一个佛教徒，<span class="_ _3"></span>我再次呼吁：<span class="_ _3"></span>佛</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y120 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">教道场跟旅游景点要分开。<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls33">旅游景点，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="ls25">可以让旅游局来管理；</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y121 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">而佛教道场，<span class="_ _b"></span>谁都可以去，<span class="_ _a"></span>不用买门票。<span class="_ _b"></span>进了佛教道场以后，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y122 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">大家不仅可以朝拜佛像，<span class="_ _9"></span>同时，<span class="_ _9"></span><span class="lse">还要有法师给他们讲经说法。<span class="_ _6"></span><span class="ls0"> </span></span></div><div class="t m0 x22 h4 y123 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">如今想了解佛法的人特别多，包括大学生等年轻一代，</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
